	   <tr><td colspan=2>The new INT / WIS cap is 355<br><br>-Cap for all stats go up by 5/level from 260 at level 61 to 280 at level 65.<br>-Innate Enlightenment 5 adds 50 to INT / WIS cap.<br>-Planar Power 5 adds 25 to all stat caps.<br><br>So for casters such as myself, the new stat cap is 355 (280+50+25) for INT and 305 (280+25) for all other stats.<br>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=209876" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=209876</a></td></tr>
